<p>The Telegraph refers to the position of Mr Brian Harrison MP (Conservative),<a href="#f3">3</a> an Australian, who is said to feel strong distaste against an immigration policy which strictly regulates the entry of Australians and grants them less favourable treatment than EEC nationals.</p>

